🧠👋 Hey friends, how are you doing today? 

As part of our commitment to supporting mental health, we're checking in with all our awesome followers to see how you're doing. 

Check in below by commenting with an emoji.

Remember, you are not alone, and seeking help is always an option. 

If you need prayer, we can pray for you. If you think you may need professional treatment for anxiety, depression, or trauma care, we can refer you to someone who can help.

W4C

rawContent:
https://t.co/BBQFT30JCM I'm not sure how I missed this, but🔥⬇️ #AmericanJournalofPsychiatry recently published a case report of a trial participant suffering from treatment-resistant #depression who responded well to #psilocybinassistedtherapy (25 mg) but DIDN'T actually trip. 

How? Turns out the fellow was taking #trazadone, a 5HT-2A blocker, so he experienced no psychedelic effects. 

For those of you who aren't necessarily keeping a close eye on the medicalization of psychedelics, the potential for tripless psychedelics to treat psychiatric patients has been hotly debated. As far as I know, none of the tripless psychedelics (or psychedelic-adjacent) drugs in development have made it to clinical trials yet. I'm sure this journal article will send an avalanche of VC cash their way. 

#psychedelics #triplesspsychedelics

To invest

Working on
What is intact,
Learning best
To distract!
